{"tid":1756080,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JYP回歸拉娜璉、多賢同台！ 被「怒吼本名吐槽」：怎這麼不會玩啊軫永","createTime":"2019-11-26T01:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T06:12:28.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4d9bd51104fa044601ffbaa27fa6a3928d8110","tid":1756080,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:27:13.000Z","msg":"南韓歌手朴軫永創立的經紀公司JYP娛樂，培育出GOT7、TWICE、Wonder Girls、2PM等人氣團體。他於1994年出道，出過不少熱門歌曲，日前宣布以新曲回歸，特地帶著TWICE成員娜璉、多賢上綜藝節目《認識的哥哥》宣傳，製作組日前釋出預告，在遊戲環節因為多賢脫口直呼他本名，製造了許多笑料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4535/d4535008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4535%2Fd4535008.jpg&h=e7a08416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朴軫永帶著娜璉及多賢上《認識的哥哥》。（圖／翻攝YouTube／JTBC Entertainment）<br />\n<br />\n朴軫永此次回歸，娜璉、多賢身為TWICE中的綜藝擔當，義氣相挺為社長站台，讓他笑稱「孩子成功了，我也沾沾光不過分吧」。其中在戴著耳機看嘴型猜謎的環節，似乎因為他一直猜不中答案，讓多賢用非敬語火大地喊「怎麼這麼不會玩啊！軫永啊！」（《認識的哥哥》節目裡主持人、來賓之間都是講非敬語），令在現場的人一陣爆笑，「笑果十足」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4535/d4535009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4535%2Fd4535009.jpg&h=2b0a8488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲多賢受不了社長猜不中答案，火大地說「怎麼這麼不會玩」。（圖／翻攝YouTube／JTBC Entertainment）<br />\n<br />\n預告釋出後，網友紛紛回應「太期待這集了」、「多賢好可愛，笑死我」、「JYP慌張的樣子太好笑」、「『沾孩子的光』明明是超有道理的話，不知道為啥從朴軫永嘴裡講出來特別搞笑」。此集節目預計將於30日晚間播出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd777395102206cd07e0a46ad3b79d957681e438","tid":1756080,"uid":309357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"開台自己打飛幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657d124b9ed68d9937ceeab2b5c1b371cdc41208","tid":1756080,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:35:30.000Z","msg":"JYP爸爸真係好玩得..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caab2ae719523f955343624fd5ca4872519a4cf5","tid":1756080,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"突然意識到自己強烈地渴望被多腎罵..."},{"pid":"12c6aeb50232af20b4fb2fd7ad724d8e3aeca0f8","tid":1756080,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:39:22.000Z","msg":"陣間多腎會唔會又屈娜璉蝦佢..."},{"pid":"463b21576722d4dd44dcccc1609db5fcd401c287","tid":1756080,"uid":222155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:39:29.000Z","msg":"娜璉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a30642a1354cf365560303a8fde993f43268b0e","tid":1756080,"uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"無定延唔睇"},{"pid":"b7e71627b8bbf91a1475e3641b11227548145438","tid":1756080,"uid":222155,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"12c6aeb50232af20b4fb2fd7ad724d8e3aeca0f8","tid":1756080,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:39:22.000Z","msg":"陣間多腎會唔會又屈娜璉蝦佢..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:40:25.000Z","msg":"條八婆一定啦，成L日扮晒可憐咁"},{"pid":"0a528a351024c70625bcef8cf01d95edda020134","tid":1756080,"uid":89660,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"caab2ae719523f955343624fd5ca4872519a4cf5","tid":1756080,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"突然意識到自己強烈地渴望被多腎罵..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:44:32.000Z","msg":"怎麼會認錯我的屁蛋啊！啊....c8"},{"pid":"21a1a2778d44b7b0862b49b1d9180a36b8674860","tid":1756080,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caab2ae719523f955343624fd5ca4872519a4cf5","tid":1756080,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"突然意識到自己強烈地渴望被多腎罵..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201